Ekaṃ  samayaṃ bhagavā kimilāyaṃkimbilāyaṃ 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='3', original='kimbilāyaṃ (sī. pī.) a. ni. 6.40; 7.59', type='auto', previous=' samayaṃ bhagavā kimilāyaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='kimilāyaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. pī.', text='kimbilāyaṃ'}}
 viharati veḷuvane. Atha kho āyasmā kimilokimbilo 
Note { id=1, line='12', referenceLine='3', original='kimbilo (sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)', type='auto', previous=' viharati veḷuvane. Atha kho āyasmā kimilo '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='kimilo'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.', text='kimbilo'}}
yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā kimilo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca – ‘‘ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hotī’’ti? ‘‘Idha, kimila, tathāgate parinibbute bhikkhū bhikkhuniyo upāsakā upāsikāyo satthari agāravā viharanti appatissā, dhamme agāravā viharanti appatissā, saṅghe agāravā viharanti appatissā, sikkhāya agāravā viharanti appatissā, aññamaññaṃ agāravā viharanti appatissā. Ayaṃ kho, kimila, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hotī’’ti.

‘‘Pañcime , bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā dhammassavane. Katame pañca? Assutaṃ suṇāti , sutaṃ pariyodāpeti, kaṅkhaṃ vitarativihanati 
Note { id=2, line='21', referenceLine='6', original='vihanati (syā. kaṃ. pī. ka.)', type='auto', previous=', sutaṃ pariyodāpeti, kaṅkhaṃ vitarati '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='vitarati'}
	Alternative{lang='syā. kaṃ. pī. ka.', text='vihanati'}}
, diṭṭhiṃ ujuṃ karoti, cittamassa pasīdati. Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā dhammassavane’’ti. Dutiyaṃ.

‘‘Pañcahi , bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadrobhaddo 
Note { id=3, line='30', referenceLine='8', original='bhaddo (pī.)', type='auto', previous=', bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='bhadro'}
	Alternative{lang='pī.', text='bhaddo'}}
assājānīyo rājāraho hoti rājabhoggo, rañño aṅgantveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati.

a. ni. 9.72; dī. ni. 3.320cetovinibaddhā (sāratthadīpanīṭīkāyaṃ). Katame pañca? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāmesu avītarāgoavigatarāgo 
Note { id=7, line='53', referenceLine='17', original='avigatarāgo (ka.)', type='auto', previous='. Katame pañca? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāmesu avītarāgo '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='avītarāgo'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='avigatarāgo'}}
hoti avigatacchando avigatapemo avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho. Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāmesu avītarāgo hoti avigatacchando avigatapemo avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, ayaṃ paṭhamo cetasovinibandho.

